urls.description: Barstool MRags is primarily an FPS player that currently enjoys playing Call of Duty: Warzone, Valorant and Halo Infinite. He has been streaming and creating gaming-related content since 2016. MRags uses a default controller, but plays with a "claw" styled grip (no back paddles).
